casebody.data:
No. 10-6652. Christopher Hayden, et ux., Petitioners v. Anthony E. D’Amico, et al. 562 U.S. 1059, 131 S. Ct. 685,

178 L. Ed. 2d 474,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9185, November 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma paup-*475eris denied. Petitioner is allowed until December 20, 2010, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
